title: The 1994 Mega-Movie Draft
description:
We are drafting again! And this time, the roster is growing. Shea Serrano and Van Lathan join Sean, Amanda, and Chris Ryan for a draft of one of the greatest years in movie history: 1994. 

Hosts: Sean Fennessey and Amanda Dobbins
Guests: Chris Ryan, Van Lathan, Shea Serrano
